job.title: Rajasthan Police SI/ Platoon Commander Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for various vacancies in Rajasthan
job.body:
Total vacancies:81

Name of the Vacancies:

  • SI/ Platoon Commander

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Graduates has been published by Rajasthan Police for SI/ Platoon Commander vacancies in Rajasthan. If you are searching for a government job in Rajasthan then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of SI/ Platoon Commander, from 30-06-2021, and till 14-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Rajasthan and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for category Gen of Rajasthan Domicile candidates is only Rs. 400/-
  • The application fee for category SC/ ST/ of Rajasthan Domicile candidates is only Rs. 350/-
  • The application fee for category Gen (Annual Income is less than 2.5 Lakh) candidates is only Rs. 350/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a SI/ Platoon Commander in Rajasthan Police, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 30-06-2021
  • ﻿ The last date to apply in these posts is 14-07-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

Rajasthan Police SI/ Platoon Commander Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for Rajasthan Police SI/ Platoon Commander Recruitment 2021? 

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the SI/ Platoon Commander. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of Rajasthan Police and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Rajasthan Police 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
